{"lastModified":1772032302796,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::bd173cf0-ab43-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia, Italy\n\nRent Aquila 50 in Cannigione, Northern Sardinia. Discover the future of marine exploration with the latest model of AQUILA power catamarans. Aquila 50 Yacht Power Catamaran redefines the concept of luxury and comfort at sea, offering top-notch innovation and style for your next Sardinian holiday. It stands out for its modern and functional design, featuring a layout with 3 cabins and 3 bathrooms, including a spacious full-beam owner’s cabin on a single level, providing sophisticated and welcoming living spaces. The exterior spaces are designed for guest entertainment, with an expanded flybridge enhanced by an optional retractable sunshade, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the Mediterranean sunshine. Powered by two Volvo Penta D6 engines of 480 hp each, the Aquila 50 ensures smooth sailing and outstanding performance. Sailing through the crystal-clear waters of Northern Sardinia aboard this rental power catamaran promises an unforgettable experience. From the islands of the La Maddalena Archipelago to the hidden coves of the Costa Smeralda, every moment is filled with relaxation and discovery.","blueprint":{"name":"AQUILA 50","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd173cf0-ab43-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::b8fa1cd0-b676-11ef-8a32-111872bb76da/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd173cf0-ab43-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::b8d66830-b676-11ef-8a32-111872bb76da/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd173cf0-ab43-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::b90c1e30-b676-11ef-8a32-111872bb76da/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd173cf0-ab43-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::f877ed60-b676-11ef-8250-3930d1c7c46c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bd173cf0-ab43-11ef-a71d-634b4f3da2c0::assets::f889eec0-b676-11ef-8250-3930d1c7c46c/{imageVariant